Package: rmdd
Title: Tools for Name Resolution with the Mammal Diversity Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Package", "Maintainer", , "your_email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a starting framework for a tidyverse-style package
    that downloads, reads, validates, and matches mammal taxonomic names
    against the Mammal Diversity Database (MDD). The package is designed
    to support a mammal-focused workflow analogous to plant-oriented
    taxonomic name resolution services.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://www.mammaldiversity.org/
BugReports: https://www.mammaldiversity.org/
